<p>To introduce green NFT solutions, you can start by exploring platforms that have implemented eco-conscious initiatives. Look for marketplaces that use blockchain networks with lower energy consumption, such as proof-of-stake (PoS) or proof-of-authority (PoA).</p>



<p>Additionally, you can seek out NFTs that support environmental causes or are created using renewable energy sources.</p>



